The paper discusses a visual analytics tool for discovering deep learning models, which falls under the categories of artificial intelligence (cs.AI), machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), human-computer interaction (cs.HC), and social and information networks (cs.SI). However, since the focus is on deep learning models, cs.AI and cs.LG are the most likely categories, followed by cs.CV, which deals with image and video analysis. The paper also discusses the user interface and interaction design of the tool, which falls under cs.HC, and the exploration of the parameter space, which falls under cs.SI.
